fr.sii.ogham.core.sender

Class FillerSender

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sii.ogham.core.sender.FillerSender
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConditionalSender, MessageSender

    public class FillerSender
extends Object
implements ConditionalSender
    Decorator sender that adds extra information to the message. This sender relies on a MessageFiller to add extra information on the message. Once filler has done its job, this sender delegates the real sending to the decorated sender.
